<ab facs="#facs_258_r1l4"><expan>woche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeıd niht ſunderheıt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> / alſo warten </ab>
