<ab facs="#facs_258_r1l7">vehe . <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vmb vns . noch alls </ab>
