<ab facs="#facs_258_line_1577192595941_1437"><expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_258_r1l11"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Jubılate </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_257" id="127v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Gmeiner reichs stette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynung</expan> in
                                <expan>Swobe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als sie auf disz zeit zu Ulme
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyn </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, ewr <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, die ir auf disz zeit zu uns meynt zu
                        senden, herberg zu bestellen etc., also <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        das Barthlomes Neythart, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>ratschreib<ex>er</ex></expan> befolhen, der hat uns gesagt, daz er
                        das getan hab, dabey ewr bott <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sey. Denn als
                        ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt,
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<pb facs="#facs_258" id="128r"/>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> von den
                            <expan>lewff<ex>en</ex></expan> bey und umb uns etwas <expan>zu
                                verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> etc.,
                                <add><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan></add> wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        den von Ulme in der <expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>woche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> seid
                        niht sunderheit <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan>, also warten wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>r<ex>ömischen</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>k<ex>ünigs</ex></expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, der <expan>kurfürst<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
                        zukunfte. Auch so steet die vehe <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den <expan>fürste<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> umb uns noch alls offen, daz sie
                                <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>beschedig<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>zugreiff<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> jubilate.</ab>
</div>
